6b160cc4-a5eb-40fc-97c8-9dfccb939939.title: Mourner
6b160cc4-a5eb-40fc-97c8-9dfccb939939.text: Do you have a problem traveller?

380f256c-8654-42cf-8d41-67700a1c5b86.title: <player>
380f256c-8654-42cf-8d41-67700a1c5b86.text:
No, I just wondered why you're wearing that outfit...
Is it fancy dress?

cb29620f-1ae6-4fe6-85f0-7e3c70481671.title: Mourner
cb29620f-1ae6-4fe6-85f0-7e3c70481671.text: Hmmm, ok then. Be on your way.

5ef4d9b3-6ff6-43a7-ae06-ae5862c4ceca.title: Mourner
5ef4d9b3-6ff6-43a7-ae06-ae5862c4ceca.text:
I'm a mourner. It's my job to help heal the plague
victims of West Ardougne and to make sure the disease
is contained.

c8de7621-95c7-4145-be6c-a562f10b15da.title: Mourner
c8de7621-95c7-4145-be6c-a562f10b15da.text:
If you come down with any symptoms such as flu or
nightmares let me know immediately.

6728d71f-3ba8-4ab9-9249-5356e21ebe3b.title: Mourner
6728d71f-3ba8-4ab9-9249-5356e21ebe3b.text: Have you experienced any plague symptoms?

options.text: No, but can you tell me where the plague came from?

a6e6204f-a1cb-42c9-9fc5-6d8990510983.title: <player>
a6e6204f-a1cb-42c9-9fc5-6d8990510983.text: No, but can you tell me where the plague came from?

be03596b-7f5e-4398-b74c-0924dd80c448.title: Mourner
be03596b-7f5e-4398-b74c-0924dd80c448.text:
It all started when King Tyras of West Ardougne
came back from one of his visits to the lands west of
here.

74d14096-aadb-4148-b0b9-dea41f906bfc.title: Mourner
74d14096-aadb-4148-b0b9-dea41f906bfc.text:
Some of his men must have unknowingly caught it out
there and brought it back with them

e6f3bd6d-648d-4584-92d2-485ce4b4586c.title: Mourner
e6f3bd6d-648d-4584-92d2-485ce4b4586c.text:
Well if you take a turn for the worse let me know
straight away.

6c739f6a-c62d-43fb-a1f7-c6b9c398a11a.title: Mourner
6c739f6a-c62d-43fb-a1f7-c6b9c398a11a.text: No... But you will have to be treated.

78c26b3a-a544-41db-ae98-857dc5a10850.title: Mourner
78c26b3a-a544-41db-ae98-857dc5a10850.text:
We have to take measures to contain the disease. That's
why you must let us know immediately if you take a
turn for the worse.

4ffbaf04-7b9e-4304-b63b-6af12c2495dd.title: Mourner
4ffbaf04-7b9e-4304-b63b-6af12c2495dd.text:
First you'll come down with heavy flu, this is usually
followed by horrifying nightmares.

5770f027-ed07-4666-8e0d-38622becb619.title: <player>
5770f027-ed07-4666-8e0d-38622becb619.text: I used to have nightmares when I was younger.

04ba1039-dfcd-4581-983a-e3142b7883de.title: Mourner
04ba1039-dfcd-4581-983a-e3142b7883de.text:
Not like these I assure you. Soon after a thick black
liquid will seep from your nose and eyes.

6823d36c-fd6a-45d2-b6e4-245c198149e7.title: Mourner
6823d36c-fd6a-45d2-b6e4-245c198149e7.text:
When it gets to that stage there's nothing we can do
for you.

26baa774-7305-4c0d-a634-be89ed4a19a0.title: Mourner
26baa774-7305-4c0d-a634-be89ed4a19a0.text:
If I find you attempting to cross the wall I'll make sure
you never return.

4a27c0a1-11b0-4cf8-b848-ff56773c25bd.title: Mourner
4a27c0a1-11b0-4cf8-b848-ff56773c25bd.text: What are you up to with old man Edmond?

3163e85c-c8ba-411c-80ab-edd8982039dd.title: <player>
3163e85c-c8ba-411c-80ab-edd8982039dd.text: Oh, you know about that then?

b16a8419-2e66-4063-93fc-19f7c995bd21.title: Mourner
b16a8419-2e66-4063-93fc-19f7c995bd21.text:
We know about everything that goes on in Ardougne.
We have to if we are to contain the plague.

0153f8d6-167c-42c7-985e-ee5354e75f7e.title: <player>
0153f8d6-167c-42c7-985e-ee5354e75f7e.text: Have you see his daughter recently?

ae6080d1-df6c-4db5-ae92-375d6f246be3.title: Mourner
ae6080d1-df6c-4db5-ae92-375d6f246be3.text:
I imagine she's caught the plague. Either way she won't
be allowed out of West Ardougne, the risk is too great.

807b2c71-8667-47ec-bebc-746081e3e90e.title: Mourner
807b2c71-8667-47ec-bebc-746081e3e90e.text: Your hands are covered in mud.

8961cfa9-21b8-4aa8-b60e-1c69b9a93717.title: Mourner
8961cfa9-21b8-4aa8-b60e-1c69b9a93717.text: Funny, you don't look like the gardening type.

91b81ad3-3ede-4753-8994-1adbbe158dac.title: <player>
91b81ad3-3ede-4753-8994-1adbbe158dac.text: Oh no, I love gardening! It's my favorite pastime.
